name: Corner Street Food
address: 1360 Coney Island Ave, Brooklyn, NY 11230, USA

reviews.text: Closed but takes orders over delivery apps
I got the empanadas. They were smaller then expected but had VERY good flavor! Would get again

The best sandwich I ever had in NYC the mama schnitzel was insane the Shawarma was so juicy no sauce was needed and meatballs soft and flavorful And the best Kabab I ever had like in my childhood in Israel .
The service by shining was superb and warm.
You can’t be in the neighborhood and not stop for a meal.

This food is nothing special for the above average/high price for the quality of the goods. Possible, since it's labeled as kosher it accounts for half of it. The other half, I would assume, is just.... unnecessary for profits. The food tastes average, but it tastes more "natural"  and home-made instead of mass factory produced. I saw all the 5 star reviews and all good comments, but ....this place only deserves 3 stars currently. I would neither reccomend or de-reccomend to somebody to come here. Want okay food for slighly above average prices and want to try a new spot? Ideal , but not something you should come back to every week. - Artur Stanistaw Siedlecki.
Really the best new local delivery place I’ve tried in the last 2 years…
Great food, changes each day which means great variety! Employees are attentive to needs and quick to fix any issue. Love the place can even take my family. I Will definitely recommend.
I when to eat with my family and the food was really good and loved they’re service. I will recommend you all you go and checkout the place and food. I will go back second time for sure.

Excellent  !!!!! Very clean place. Everything there is fresh. looks & smells so delicious !! I took Moroccan meatballs sandwich. With the Moroccan focaccia bread ( Frena )
With hummus & schug & vegetables.  it was extraordinary  !!!! It was just Woooow !!!!! Highly recommended  ! Definitely will order again !!
Love this place not for its very simple decor or style. The food is tasty and large portions are served very fresh. Overall great service.
